title: Stefan und Bully gegen irgendson Schnulli
overview: For the first time ever, entertainment heavyweights Stefan Raab and Michael 'Bully' Herbig are competing as a duo on a game show. Who will come out on top? Their opponents could be tradesmen, doctors, students, teachers or lawyers. Raab and Bully will compete against the candidate who manages to beat three other contestants at the start of the show. Elton will host the new show, with Frank Buschmann providing commentary.
